articles.title: Australia vs Pakistan Semifinal U19 World Cup: AUS beat PAK by 1 wicket - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Australia vs Pakistan U19 World Cup 2024, AUS vs PAK: Australia have set a rematch of the 2023 ODI World Cup final with India in South Africa.
